articles.author: Cristina Gallardo
articles.title: Rishi Sunak heads to Northern Ireland to sell imminent Brexit deal - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Officials say a deal is likely as early as Tuesday but could still fall apart in the coming days.
articles.content:
LONDON U.K. Prime Minister Rishi Sunak is traveling to Northern Ireland to meet local politicians as a deal with the EU on a long-running post-Brexit trade row looms.
